tialiased; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">5月15日晚，阿里影业发出公告称，旗下售票业务平台淘宝电影获17亿元人民币的A轮融资。这轮融资后，淘宝电影的整体估值达到137亿元。</p><p class=\"text\" style=\"margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 25px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-family: arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, 微软雅黑, MicrosoftYaHei, 宋体, 宋体, Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, STHeiti; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">淘宝电影2014年年底才上线，在目前的主流在线购票平台中算是成立时间最短的一家。</p><p class=\"text\" style=\"margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 25px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-family: arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, 微软雅黑, MicrosoftYaHei, 宋体, 宋体, Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, STHeiti; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">虽然时间短，但2015年淘宝电影以发行、票务合作等多种方式与包括《碟中谍5》、《寻龙诀》、《夏洛特烦恼》在内的84部影片进行合作，合作影片票房总量达到226亿元，占2015年全国总票房超50%。</p><p class=\"text\" style=\"margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 25px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-family: arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, 微软雅黑, MicrosoftYaHei, 宋体, 宋体, Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, STHeiti; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">2015年年底，阿里影业又从阿里集团收购了淘宝电影业务，整合之后，淘宝电影已成阿里影业宣传发行板块的重要部分。</p><p class=\"text\" style=\"margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 25px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-family: arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, 微软雅黑, MicrosoftYaHei, 宋体, 宋体, Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, STHeiti; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">淘宝电影的这轮A轮融资，除了鼎晖投资1家是VC机构，其他都是上市公司或者大公司，领投的大公司有蚂蚁金服、新浪网，跟投的则是5家影视公司：</p><p class=\"text\" style=\"margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 25px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-family: arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, 微软雅黑, MicrosoftYaHei, 宋体, 宋体, Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, STHeiti; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">博纳影业、华策影视，《美人鱼》两家保底发行方和和影业和联瑞影业，还有南派三叔的南派泛娱。</p><p class=\"text\" style=\"margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 25px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-family: arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, 微软雅黑, MicrosoftYaHei, 宋体, 宋体, Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, STHeiti; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">看来，淘宝电影的野心也早已经不是单纯卖个票了。</p><p class=\"text\" style=\"margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 25px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-family: arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, 微软雅黑, MicrosoftYaHei, 宋体, 宋体, Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, STHeiti; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 800; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\">有野心的不止淘宝，微影时代也刚完成一轮巨额融资</span></p><p class=\"text\" style=\"margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 25px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-family: arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, 微软雅黑, MicrosoftYaHei, 宋体, 宋体, Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, STHeiti; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">巧合的是前不久，还有一家在线票务巨头也才刚完成了一个大动作。</p><p class=\"text\" style=\"margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 25px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-family: arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, 微软雅黑, MicrosoftYaHei, 宋体, 宋体, Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, STHeiti; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">4月26日，微影时代宣布完成了30亿元的C+轮融资，算上此前15亿元的C轮融资，C轮的两次融资就让这个公司收获了45亿元人民币，公司估值达20亿美元。</p><p class=\"text\" style=\"margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 25px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-family: arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, 微软雅黑, MicrosoftYaHei, 宋体, 宋体, Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, STHeiti; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">看来淘宝电影这轮融资，跟微影时代对标的意味可不小，但淘宝电影可刚刚才A轮融资。</p><p class=\"text\" style=\"margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 25px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-family: arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, 微软雅黑, MicrosoftYaHei, 宋体, 宋体, Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, STHeiti; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">其实如果加上微影时代旗下的微影资本还有接近60亿元资金储备，微影时代是有了100亿元资本的来玩这个泛娱乐市场的。</p><p class=\"text\" style=\"margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 25px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-family: arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, 微软雅黑, MicrosoftYaHei, 宋体, 宋体, Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, STHeiti; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">微影时代的前身是微票儿，2014年迄今为止已经完成四轮融资，背后站着的是腾讯、万达、华人控股等多家互联网巨头和娱乐圈大佬，也是难怪这么豪。</p><p class=\"text\" style=\"margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 25px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-family: arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, 微软雅黑, MicrosoftYaHei, 宋体, 宋体, Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, STHeiti; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">但成立近两年的微影时代，也早已经不是当初那个单纯卖票的。</p><p class=\"text\" style=\"margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 25px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-family: arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, 微软雅黑, MicrosoftYaHei, 宋体, 宋体, Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, STHeiti; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">在票务领域，微影时代旗下拥有双平台了微票儿与格瓦拉；演出领域，则拥有一站式服务平台小格娱乐；体育领域，拆分成立的新品牌微赛体育已经独立运作，A轮融资后估值也已经达12亿人民币；数据领域，则拥有实时票房分析系统微票儿票房分析APP。</p><p class=\"text\" style=\"margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 25px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-family: arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, 微软雅黑, MicrosoftYaHei, 宋体, 宋体, Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, STHeiti; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 800; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\">卖票的平台有多火，BAT已经开启三国杀</span></p><p class=\"text\" style=\"margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 25px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-family: arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, 微软雅黑, MicrosoftYaHei, 宋体, 宋体, Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, STHeiti; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">为啥这些卖票的平台可以发展到如今这个局势，DT君来跟你好好聊一聊。</p><p class=\"text\" style=\"margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 25px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-family: arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, 微软雅黑, MicrosoftYaHei, 宋体, 宋体, Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, STHeiti; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">首先是中国的电影市场如此兴盛，卖票的平台自然也是热火朝天。</p><p class=\"text\" style=\"margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 25px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-family: arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, 微软雅黑, MicrosoftYaHei, 宋体, 宋体, Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, STHeiti; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">也许你不知道，互联网和电影产业都很发达的美国，线上票房比例只有20%，而在中国2015年这个数字高达57.5%。</p><p class=\"text\" style=\"margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 25px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-family: arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, 微软雅黑, MicrosoftYaHei, 宋体, 宋体, Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, STHeiti; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">在中国，这个领域的竞争者除了院线自营的票务平台，还有一些是自带O2O基因的，以及基于电影社区发展起来的平台。</p><p class=\"image\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: medium; font-family: arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, 微软雅黑, MicrosoftYaHei, 宋体, 宋体, Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, STHeiti; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://d.hiphotos.baidu.com/news/w%3D638/sign=66c5a123b5fb43161a1f797918a54642/2934349b033b5bb59242e11631d3d539b700bc45.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; display: inline-block; max-width: 680px;\"/></p><p class=\"text\" style=\"margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 25px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-family: arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, 微软雅黑, MicrosoftYaHei, 宋体, 宋体, Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, STHeiti; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">而且，在这个被BAT统治的中国互联网界，这些票务平台一个个也都是他们三家的。</p><p class=\"text\" style=\"margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 25px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-family: arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, 微软雅黑, MicrosoftYaHei, 宋体, 宋体, Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, STHeiti; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">比如，腾讯旗下的微票儿和格瓦拉，以及新美大下面的大众点评和猫眼电影，阿里的淘宝电影以及百度的百度糯米。</p><p class=\"text\" style=\"margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 25px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-family: arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, 微软雅黑, MicrosoftYaHei, 宋体, 宋体, Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, STHeiti; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">除了百度糯米，其他几家卖票的大平台都已经开始独立运作。</p><p class=\"text\" style=\"margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 25px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-family: arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, 微软雅黑, MicrosoftYaHei, 宋体, 宋体, Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, STHeiti; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">多亏了这些财大气粗的金主，各种票补撑起了电影票O2O的半边天。</p><p class=\"text\" style=\"margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 25px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-family: arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, 微软雅黑, MicrosoftYaHei, 宋体, 宋体, Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, STHeiti; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">这次淘宝电影，17亿融资到手，而此前微影C轮和C+轮融资总额也达到了45亿元，这似乎意味着新一轮票补即将开启。</p><p class=\"text\" style=\"margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 25px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-family: arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, 微软雅黑, MicrosoftYaHei, 宋体, 宋体, Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, STHeiti; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 800; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\">你以为这些O2O真的只是卖电影票的？图森破</span></p><p class=\"text\" style=\"margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 25px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-family: arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, 微软雅黑, MicrosoftYaHei, 宋体, 宋体, Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, STHeiti; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">真心不要以为金主们是乱撒钱，2015年，其实中国主要第三方在线票务平台都已经全面参与电影投资、营销发行、影院服务、衍生品销售和版权运营等各个环节。</p><p class=\"text\" style=\"margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 25px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-family: arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, 微软雅黑, MicrosoftYaHei, 宋体, 宋体, Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, STHeiti; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">他们通过在上游为制片方、下游为影院提供各种服务，已经成为了电影宣传、发行及售票的重要入口。</p><p class=\"image\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: medium; font-family: arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, 微软雅黑, MicrosoftYaHei, 宋体, 宋体, Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, STHeiti; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://a.hiphotos.baidu.com/news/w%3D638/sign=599848e95b6034a829e2bb82f31149d9/94cad1c8a786c917bf8393d1ce3d70cf3ac75752.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; display: inline-block; max-width: 680px;\"/></p><p class=\"text\" style=\"margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 25px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-family: arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, 微软雅黑, MicrosoftYaHei, 宋体, 宋体, Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, STHeiti; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">上面的模式你们看起来可能有点虚，那接下来看点实在的栗子……</p><p class=\"text\" style=\"margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 25px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-family: arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, 微软雅黑, MicrosoftYaHei, 宋体, 宋体, Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, STHeiti; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 800; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\">玩发行！在线票务平台已是高票房影片的“标配”</span></p><p class=\"text\" style=\"margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 25px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-family: arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, 微软雅黑, MicrosoftYaHei, 宋体, 宋体, Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, STHeiti; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">从发行来看，2015年国产电影票房前十的影片中，在线票务平台参与发行的影片占到了9部之多。</p><p class=\"image\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: medium; font-family: arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, 微软雅黑, MicrosoftYaHei, 宋体, 宋体, Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, STHeiti; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-align: center; letter-spacin